net.antidot.api.upload

Class MultipartEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractHttpEntity
      • net.antidot.api.upload.MultipartEntity

  • public class MultipartEntity
extends AbstractHttpEntity
    Multi-parts entity.

    Lighttpd (version 1.4.28 and 1.4.31) does not support chunked data. So we provide our own multi-parts entity to send multi-parts data in one data block with known size.
